@startuml
' IOD(10)_Pj2_T-1 — User Story 10: View Detailed Class Information
' Author: MayfairMI6

skinparam DefaultFontName Arial
skinparam ActivityBackgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam ActivityBorderColor #444444
skinparam ArrowColor #444444
skinparam NoteBackgroundColor #FFFFCC
skinparam NoteBorderColor #AAAAAA

title IOD(10)_Pj2_T-1\nUS10: View Detailed Class Information

note right: Author: MayfairMI6

start

:Prerequisite: schedule data has been imported\n(see US1 — Upload Excel File);

:Actor navigates to the Search & Filter Classes Page;

:Actor enters search criteria to locate a specific class\n(e.g., course code, instructor name, semester);

#ADD8E6:**ref** UC_SEARCH — Search and Filter Classes
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
System queries the database and returns matching classes;

if (Results found?) then (yes)

  :System displays list of matching classes;

  :Actor selects a specific class from the results;

  #ADD8E6:**ref** UC_DETAILS — View Class Details
  ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  System retrieves and displays all attributes of the class:\nCRN, course code, title, section, credits, instructor,\nenrollment, room, meeting days, meeting times, semester;

  :Actor reviews complete class information;

else (no)
  :System displays "No results found" message;
  :Actor refines criteria and searches again;
endif

stop
@enduml
